3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach for shadow detection and removal using deep learning techniques. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and graphics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and multimedia content.
